item.title: Research
item.description: Net Telescope Lab Net Telescope Lab (NT-Lab) is a research team headed by Dr. Yen-Hung Chen, locating in National Taipei University of Nursing and Health Sciences (NTUNHS), Taipei. Focus domain We are working on: Observing significant changes in connectivity geolocated to East Asia region, Identifying large-scale events happened on the Internet, Establishing agenda, alternatives, and national/business policies
